---
title: Pan-Fried John Dory & Brown Butter Sauce with Parmesan Mash & Almond Baby Broccoli
description: There’s treasure to be found in the ocean and we’ve brought some up from the deep just for you. Plate up these dory fish fillets with a parsley butter sauce that can be soaked up in the Parmesan potato mash. Tonight is a luxurious dinner that everyone will be falling in love with.

